WEBVTT

00:00.034 --> 00:03.699
Take your Bibles, if you would, please turn to the book of Philippians chapter three.

00:04.119 --> 00:06.783
If you don't have a Bible in your hand, if you would, open up the bulletin.

00:06.803 --> 00:09.827
You're gonna find the outline for the message in the bulletin.

00:09.847 --> 00:13.492
And most of the verses are placed there for your help as well.

00:13.772 --> 00:17.177
We always wanna make sure we're following through God's word as we preach.

00:17.197 --> 00:20.922
And as we introduce our theme this morning, which is reaching forth.

00:21.382 --> 00:25.989
And today we begin a brand new sermon series entitled Let the Journey Begin.

00:26.029 --> 00:30.034
And we're gonna begin that journey and reach forth for the Lord in our new year.

00:30.018 --> 00:34.123
Tonight, we'll be introducing all of the preaching for Sunday morning, Sunday night and Wednesday night.

00:34.383 --> 00:42.533
We have a great packet for you of materials that relate to the development and the goals of the church, and you won't want to miss the time at five o'clock tonight.

